Package: taskfix
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: abdemassoune@gmail.com
Description: Transform raw task descriptions into structured tasks using AI
 TaskFix turns messy task descriptions into clean, structured, AI-formatted
 technical tasks — suitable for GitHub Issues, Jira, or any task tracker.
 .
 Configuration files:
  - System-wide: /etc/taskfix/config
  - User config: ~/.tfixrc or ~/.config/taskfix/config
